{"tid":1421364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好出北角 一出就輸","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:46.000Z","uid":82312,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8425a8372c337ebdb379b2b7ebea716b10136be2","tid":1421364,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"北角居民唔洗你地救<br />\n自己返上樓鎖好門<br />\n可以報定狗話聽到呢啲消息<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有 勇武出去只會3種情況<br />\n1.勇武打黑幫 黑幫用刀你用遮<br />\n啲狗由得你地打<br />\n打贏都自已有傷亡<br />\n<br />\n2. 出到去冇人 到時又比人話借機搞事<br />\n啲店都關晒紋做死城<br />\n示威者又輸<br />\n<br />\n3.真係有黑幫又同示威者打 狗出黎勇狗示威者 冇我地警察你地死晒啦<br />\n<br />\n4. 兩邊都拉 夠晒公平 你地冇得嘈啦<br />\n<br />\nBe water 人地搵我地我地就唔見人<br />\n大陸仔來回冇一日 撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"efcebb0f89f834f85aaed5cb97df52389bd6074f","tid":1421364,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756694a4cbe79c4480a68c0d8d008f58af6dc60","tid":1421364,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得要撚狗!!!<br />\n冷處理</span>"},{"pid":"b7e61bfa3cd550797dcb9e7e862818f3afb85a95","tid":1421364,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e384d0c5240156547f9a992a7bb718125190a2cb","tid":1421364,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"咪好似722元朗屯門咁囉，吹晒風咁多地使乜理"},{"pid":"13b45d469884f3c06da6afb06c18fb84e3480d5c","tid":1421364,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}